    http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4

    ValueWithAttributes CodeExternal

      • http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4:StringShort
        • http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4:CodeExternal

      • Description

        Code with additional information describing the code authority.

    • Example XML

      <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>

<CodeExternal description="Visa" id="codeExternal_1" name="Example String Value" uRL="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns="http://www.opentravel.org/OTM/Common/v4">Example String Value</CodeExternal>

      Example JSON

      {
  "CodeExternal" : {
    "value" : "Example String Value",
    "description" : "Visa",
    "name" : "Example String Value",
    "uRL" : "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema",
    "id" : "codeExternal_1"
  }
}

      • Attribute Summary

        Attributes 
        Name Description
        description
        Description of who manages this set of codes.
        Details
        Type http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema:string
        Example Value Visa
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        name
        This may be a source authority/ owner name, ID or code.
        Details
        Type http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema:string
        Example Value Example String Value
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        uRL
        Implementer: This is A URL to the code source authority/ owner.
        Details
        Type http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema:anyURI
        Example Value http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
        id
        Implementer: This is used for a database or key ID for the code item (if it is different from the @CodeExtension) in relationship to the obsolete code indicator.
        Details
        Type http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema:ID
        Example Value codeExternal_1
        Required false
        Pattern N/A
        Max Occurrences 1
